article_title: Pinnacle bank boosts income 19 percent after buying CapitalMark bank

article_metadata.description: Pinnacle Financial Partners, Inc., the Nashville-based banking firm that acquired CapitalMark Bank in Chattanooga this summer, boosted its third quarter earnings by 19.2 percent to 62 cents per share in the third quarter.
